snippet.title: Launch of PSLV-C57/Aditya-L1 Mission from Satish Dhawan Space Centre (SDSC) SHAR, Sriharikota
snippet.description: Aditya L1 shall be the first space based Indian mission to study the Sun. The spacecraft shall be placed in a halo orbit around the Lagrange point 1 (L1) of the Sun-Earth system, which is about 1.5 million km from the Earth. A satellite placed in the halo orbit around the L1 point has the major advantage of continuously viewing the Sun without any occultation/eclipses. This will provide a greater advantage of observing the solar activities and its effect on space weather in real time.

On their way to Satara, Team CID comes across an injured Man who reveals to them about an attacked man near the waterfall. Daya tries his best to save Abhijeet but Abhijeet falls in the waterfall. Daya finds a Camera near the waterfall. Daya, Nikhil and Shreya meet Madan's Wife. Is Madan alive or dead? Watch Now!

• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #CIDSeries #LIVCrime #NewCID #LatestCID #Crime 

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: ISRO's Aditya L1 Mission: India's Maiden Sun Mission Lifts Off | Aditya L1 Launch | Sun Mission
snippet.description:
ISRO's Aditya L1 Mission: The Aditya L1 mission will take an approach similar to the Chandrayaan-3 mission. It will first get into an Earth orbit and from there, it will go higher and faster until it eventually puts itself on a path to its final halo orbit around the first Lagrange point (L1) of the Earth and the Sun. The Lagrange point is a convenient vantage point for the probe because being around it would mean that it can remain in the same position without using a lot of fuel. This is also why the National Aeronautics and Space Administration (NASA) placed the James Webb Space Telescope at the second Lagrange point. (L2)

snippet.title: 2nd T20I | Highlights | New Zealand Tour Of England | 1st September 2023
snippet.description:
England dominated with both bat and ball in the second T20I against New Zealand. England batted first and posted a massive total of 198 runs thanks to Bairstow and Brook's sizzling knocks. New Zealand lost both their openers quickly during the chase and soon the other batters followed. England bowlers were outstanding as they bowled out New Zealand for just 103 and won the match by 95 runs.

snippet.description:

Lyrics: 
Nusta paisa 
Phir kya bolti company 
Sabko Psy

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa
                   
Meku test mat kar, mein marta ghar dar
Ye diss karra gandu, iska vishaych karta 
Teku dikhna pasand hai re bro, mein shaat nai dikhta 
Mala diss karto aai ghalaya, rukh tere pech likhta 

Mein abhi bade bade logo me, uthta baithta 
Aur tu shemde kider toh pan, fukte baithta
Teko score karne paise nai, mein haste chuthta
Meko malum hai re bro, tu meku copy karta

Arrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr
Tu phele se kele, bhonda dikhta 
Teku phele pan bola tha, tu bhonda likhta 
Fir kya kaaju pista, aeedha gand me ghusta 
Mein sirf gaane likhta, ann sirf notaa ginta

Tu mera fan nai hai bruh, lekin show pe dikhta
Tu like karta lavde photo khudka 
Mein nai marta sutta 
Mein meri maa ki sunnta 
Teku kon nai sunnta
Ann tu kya pan sunnta 

Tu classes k bhar rukh k, madhiya dhoondta 
Mein carti sunnta, ann tu g** sunnta 
Tu dhating karta, ann mein shooting karta
Mein phele ke dost log se, baat nai karta

Tu hai balish buddi, mein shartir ladka 
Tu hate karta meku, aur mein party karta 
1 week me 3 4 bar, shopping karta
Tu ladki log ke number se, message karta

Teku malum meri capacity 
Mein marte chutha matlab 
!! appa !!
Mi haanat soot to 
Pucchi wani tondacha, tu kai pan bolto 
Tumcha aai cha puccha, tumchya gang lach kolto

Arey call uchal ki shattu ji, stanny boltoy
Kiti vela bollo Tula Nadi nako lagu
Ayee D yho aplay la, vadiuu boltoy
Ghalun takal Tula, svata stanny boltoy

Tumlog ye jo karre na, usko planning bolte hai
Logo ko tum bolne do, woh log kya bhi bolte
Mi aai zavto one side, isleye stanny bolte 
Opp la deun taku, ye kai padri 
Ghosta ae

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Mera paisa mere jaisa 
Iska paisa uska paisa

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa
Iska paisa uska paisa 

Tadiwala road, tadi peeta mera homie
Phatki nikla mera khas, mera kattar homie 
Phele kaise thi woh, meku milke change hogayi
Meku pasand nai hai drama, aur woh daily roti 

Only fans unki ban gayeli hai, rozi roti
Squat marke tu hogayeli kitni patli
Mere saath poora india, meri hawa hogayi
Mein bhi rehta teri jaga pe, toh jalan hoti

Shhhhhhhhhhhhhh !!!!

Lafde hogaye mere uss din , daru biru pk
Aage jaana chahte log, mein jana chahta peeche 
Ghumayega mein ek ko, sablog hojayege peeche 
Bich me tere Homie ka, gir gayela wicket

Smoke karu teku jaisa pop smoke vishayyy
Focus karu paise pe, aati uss se bitches
Haath chodho sirf, jab bhi opps log dikhe
Pull up karu shitt, jab bhi cops log dikhe

Yede ki ko woh lera tha, maine bola theek haiiiiiiiii

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS! HAALAND HAT-TRICK HELPS CITY BACK TO PREMIER LEAGUE SUMMIT | Man City 5 1 Fulham
snippet.description:
An Erling Haaland hat-trick helped City move back to the Premier League summit and maintain our 100% start to the 2023/24 campaign with a 5-1 win over Fulham at the Etihad Stadium.
The Norwegian's seventh treble in sky blue rounded off a remarkable week for our number nine, whose first of the afternoon saw him become the quickest player to 40 Premier League goals.
Julian Alvarez had handed City the lead on the half hour, but the visitors replied almost instantly through Tim Ream.
But Nathan Ake headed home on the stroke of half-time to restore our advantage, despite heavy protests from the Fulham players and coaching staff who felt Manuel Akanji had interfered from an offside position.
After the break, though, Haaland took centre stage to see City into the international break in style.

snippet.title: Jawan: Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya | Shah Rukh Khan | Atlee | Anirudh | Nayanthara | Vishal D | Shilpa R
snippet.description:
Get ready to groove like never before as "Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya", the latest dance track from the highly-anticipated Atlee directorial, Jawan, is out now. The film stars Shah Rukh Khan, Vijay Sethupathi, Nayanthara, and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance) and is set to release in cinemas on September 7, 2023, in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu!

#NotRamaiyaVastavaiya out now!

♪Full Song Available on♪

Lyrics:

Dance with me now I can’t break away
Aaj sari fikreiin tu shake away
Shake away
Dil thirakta dance wale groove pe
Nachun mai to step mera vekh ve

Vekh ve
Aaj sare kaam kal pe talke
Tak dhina dhin nache jayein taal pe
Disko jaz blues sare bhoolke
Desi wale geet pe tu jhoolke
Pehle kiya chaiya chaiya re
Ab kar tha tha thaiyya
Ramiya vasta vaiya..!
Antra

Sama mazedar hua houle houle
Thoda nashedar hua
Man ye dole
Aaj koi nachta hua sa jadu
Sar pe swar hua
Dil ye bole
Doobi khushiyon mein
Raat apni jabse suraj dhala
Chodh sharmana aaj nachle pair chakkle zara

Pahle kiya chaiya chaiiya re
Ab kar tata thaiya
Ramiya vasta vaiyaa..!

Episode 3866: Jetha Ke Peeth Piche Hua Drama
--------------------------------------------------------
When Jethalal returns to the Gokuldham society, he finds no one in the society. He goes to check at Taarak's place but receives no response, he believes that the members must have gone to a picnic without him. Bhide updates him on what transpired while he was away. Jethalal gets angry after listening to how Bapuji was treated by Danger bhai and hails Inspector Chaalu Pandey for helping his beloved father. Later, Chintamani visits the Gokuldham community with a new medical issue. What's next for Dr. Hathi?

snippet.description:
Dastak Mayray Dil Pay Episode 129 also called Sencal Kapimi or You Knock on my Door is a Turkish Drama in Urdu Dubbing dated 3 September 2023

🎉 Subscribe @Urdu1Officialchannel Youtube Channel and don't forget to click the Bell icon  , you'll be the first to know about our new uploads, behind-the-scenes content . Join us on this journey, and let's create amazing memories together!

#urdu1 #sencalkapimi #dastakmayraydilpay 

Eda is a bright, beautiful young woman working part time with her florist Aunt. She dreams of getting her degree and moving to Italy, but her dreams are shattered when the heir to the Bolat Holding Company cancels her scholarship. 

Now only two things keep her going - her love of flowers and her hatred for Serkan Bolat. When Serkan comes to speak at Eda’s university, Eda protests strongly. A series of events then leaves these two handcuffed together for most of the day when Eda learns that Serkan really is everything she hates: arrogant, self-centred and a complete control freak. 

When the media mistakenly links the two, Serkan plans to use Eda to get his ex-girlfriend back who had left him and got engaged to another man. The unlikely pair come to an agreement. Eda will pretend to be Serkan’s fiancée, and he will restore her scholarship in return. The arrangement will only last for a couple of months until his ex’s wedding but pretending to be the fiancée of Istanbul’s most eligible bachelor turns out to be a lot harder than Eda has imagined.

snippet.title: Teacher's Day Ki Tayari | Syllabus Ke Doosri Aur! | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Get ready for a heartwarming and hilarious ride as we present "Teacher's Day Ki Tayari" - a delightful comedy sketch that celebrates the innocence, mischief, and the genuine love that school kids have for their teachers.
In this charming sketch, we follow a group of spirited school kids who've hatched a plan to surprise their beloved teacher on Teacher's Day. As they embark on their mission, you'll find yourself reminiscing about your own school days and the joy of preparing a surprise for your favorite teacher.
Tell us about you Teacher's Day memories in the Comments!

snippet.title: Kasam Se - The Proposal | Armaan Malik & Aashna Shroff | Amaal Mallik, Kunaal Vermaa
snippet.description:
‘Kasam Se’ is a musical love letter to my better half. An ode to our love story. It’s a promise to her that no matter how difficult the circumstances, I’ll always be there holding her hand through it all. When you find your soulmate, your forever person - there’s no looking back. Aashna is the most special person in my life and I feel extremely lucky to spend the rest of my life with her. Here's to our forever!

- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

snippet.title: बंगाल की खाड़ी का लो प्रेशर किन राज्यों को भिगोएगा पंजाब, हरियाणा, राजस्थान, गुजरात बारिश का इंतजार
snippet.description:
बारिश की गतिविधियां बिहार सहित उड़ीसा झारखंड छत्तीसगढ़ और महाराष्ट्र में शुरू हो चुकी है पूर्वी मध्य प्रदेश और तेलंगाना में भी अच्छी बारिश की संभावना है। आंध्र प्रदेश, कर्नाटक और तमिलनाडु में तेज बारिश लेकिन केरल में भारी बारिश होगी। अंडमान और निकोबार दीप समूह में तेज बारिश की गतिविधियां जारी रहेगी लक्षद्वीप के भी कई भागों में अच्छी बारिश संभव है। पहाड़ों पर बारिश की गतिविधियां कम हो जाएगी। पंजाब हरियाणा दिल्ली राजस्थान और गुजरात का मौसम अभी शुष्क रहेगा 6 या 7 सितंबर को पूर्वी गुजरात और पूर्वी राजस्थान में हल्की बारिश हो सकती है।

Episode 3865: Soch Acchi Rakho
--------------------------------------------------------
Chintamani's son and daughter-in-law arrive at Gokhuldham to notify them that Chintamani has recovered. Everyone is relieved since Dr. Hathi will no longer be held accountable. Danger Bhai, like a protective sibling, video calls Chintamani to check on him. Dr. Hathi queries the hospital doctor about the drug that caused Chintamani's illness. Later, it was discovered that Chintamani was hospitalized as a result of taking online-prescribed drugs. Chintamani is later cautioned not to undertake such things in the future.

After meeting Bagha, he clarifies all the confusion which was troubling Jethalal and Nattu Kaka. At the same time, Taarak also comes to Jethalal's shop. He is informed about mis-understanding. Later, altogether have fun and have a small party in the godown. Stay tuned to get your daily dose of laughter.

Show Name : Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast: Kush Shah, Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode No: 2485
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#comedy2023 #comedy #jethalal #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: सितंबर के शुरुआती दौर में कई राज्यों में भारी बारिश की आशंका | Skymet Weather
snippet.description:
सितंबर के शुरुआती दौर में बंगाल की खाड़ी में एक निम्न दवा का क्षेत्र बन सकता है जो पश्चिम दिशा में आगे बढ़ते हुए उड़ीसा तटीय आंध्र प्रदेश तेलंगाना विदर्भ मराठवाड़ा सहित मध्य प्रदेश और छत्तीसगढ़ में तेज बारिश देगा। यह मध्य प्रदेश पर आते-आते उत्तर पूर्व की तरफ मुड़ेगा तथा फिर उत्तर प्रदेश बिहार और झारखंड में भी भारी बारिश दे सकता है। परंतु इसका प्रभाव पश्चिमी राजस्थान गुजरात और महाराष्ट्र के तटीय भागों में दिखाई नहीं देगा। पंजाब हरियाणा और दिल्ली का मौसम भी शुष्क बना रहने की संभावना है। दक्षिण भारत में मानसून एक बार फिर सक्रिय हो सकता है।

snippet.title: Ghost Hunters | Comedy | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
The country is witnessing a sudden outbreak of conjunctivitis (Eye Flu), and cases of pink eye are being reported in higher numbers. Conjunctivitis (Eye Flu), or pink eye, is an irritation or inflammation of the conjunctiva, which covers the white part of the eyeball. It can be caused by allergies or bacterial or viral infection: Conjunctivitis (Eye Flu) can be extremely contagious and is spread by contact with eye secretions from someone who is infected.
We must maintain good hygiene which includes washing hands and avoiding touching eyes with bare or unwashed hands. We must also avoid sharing personal belongings like towels, lenses, or glasses. The area where you live should be cleaned properly.
